        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>This TSI describes the freon compressor base mount on 2000, 5000, 8000 and 9000 Series vehicles
                    with 3176 Caterpillar engines and air conditioning which has been improved to prevent the freon
                    compressor drive belt from flipping off. This letter lists parts and instructions to install the
                    improved base mount on these vehicles if the freon compressor drive belt is flipping off.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
